{"tid":1370176,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【元朗黑夜】便衣及軍裝警入病房找傷者　屯院：錄口供須書面要求","createTime":"2019-07-27T02:10:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T02:33:33.000Z","uid":68738,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c761c3ff07a256504b247a15c05340812067610f","tid":1370176,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:10:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3087099/org/bb10ed7f251cc9494861597cf1170326.jpg/IS5IzscDx0IT99uVfHHESNgpYkk7xjjrFCPoXRQj6F0?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3087099%2Forg%2Fbb10ed7f251cc9494861597cf1170326.jpg%2FIS5IzscDx0IT99uVfHHESNgpYkk7xjjrFCPoXRQj6F0%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=af7e1f40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n元朗周日（21日）發生「無差別襲擊」事件之後，45名傷者曾經被送入新界西醫院聯網的三間公立醫院，部份人需留院。<br />\n<br />\n有傷者及前線醫護向《香港01》透露，有警員曾於翌日（22日）清晨進入病房，向醫護查找事件的傷者，亦曾嘗試直接向病人查問詳情，惟遭在場醫護拒絕其要求。據了解至少有3宗同類事件，發生於屯門醫院的外科病房，分別涉及軍裝警員及便衣探員。<br />\n<br />\n屯門醫院證實警方曾於元朗衝突期間派員前往醫院調查事件，但院方按實務守則，要求警方提交索取病人資料的書面要求。警察公共關係科接獲《香港01》查詢至今事隔4天，尚未有一個說法。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/356421/%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E9%BB%91%E5%A4%9C-%E4%BE%BF%E8%A1%A3%E5%8F%8A%E8%BB%8D%E8%A3%9D%E8%AD%A6%E5%85%A5%E7%97%85%E6%88%BF%E6%89%BE%E5%82%B7%E8%80%85-%E5%B1%AF%E9%99%A2-%E9%8C%84%E5%8F%A3%E4%BE%9B%E9%A0%88%E6%9B%B8%E9%9D%A2%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=mama&amp;fbclid=IwAR2VslDCMCitP0V8IlYMwiqVSAMmI3HNxOz3CNQkqkFp78QdUMaSwbvXG58\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F356421%2F%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597%25E9%25BB%2591%25E5%25A4%259C-%25E4%25BE%25BF%25E8%25A1%25A3%25E5%258F%258A%25E8%25BB%258D%25E8%25A3%259D%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2585%25A5%25E7%2597%2585%25E6%2588%25BF%25E6%2589%25BE%25E5%2582%25B7%25E8%2580%2585-%25E5%25B1%25AF%25E9%2599%25A2-%25E9%258C%2584%25E5%258F%25A3%25E4%25BE